{
  "stem": "12491.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he looks at a distant [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I explained to him that we are being taken out of ghetto every morning, put on a truck, counted, coming-- driven to the airport.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before the ramp is open to let us in, we are counted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we are assembled to go back to the ghetto, we are counted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we arrive at the ghetto again, before we are allowed to get in, we are counted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, so of course, I could not have been here overnight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he looked to the corner, to the officer who's in charge of our department at the time, and I saw him shaking his head that this how it is, that I couldn't have been here.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this is when he stood up and he said, you are free to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't play the SS game.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Something in-- to this extent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was, in my opinion, a significant thing in my life which probably saved my life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the three Polish people who worked there, never anybody heard about them anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They must have been killed-- arrested, and eventually disposed of.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, this was before we actually were living already on the airport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While living at the airport, I still continued working where I did, and things were reasonably good there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were given a reasonable amount of food, and we did good-- good work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a-- a Jewish doctor in the camp, and something happened-- the-- the Jewish doctor was ordered to give us some kind of injections which were given into your thigh.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was given that injection-- everybody did-- and it must have been an unclean needle or something that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My-- my leg swelled terribly.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
